column2: SELECT TOP # specObjID, survey, bestobjid, z /*Table of top # objects with redshift, survey they are in, and object ID for searching*/  FROM SpecObj /*Objects with spectra*/  WHERE class = &&& /* The objects shown will all be QSO&&&boss' /*searching across both the legacy and boss surveys (and not other surveys) */  AND htmid*# & # < (# * #) /* This is the randomisation algorithm - the number # represents #% of the returned data*/
